The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Jesse West, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 59048;First District (5th Division)April 11, 1974.

BARRETT, J., took no part.

Paul Bradley, Deputy Defender, of Chicago (Steven Clark, Assistant Appellate Defender, of counsel), for appellant.Bernard Carey, State’s Attorney, of Chicago (Kenneth L. Gillis and Alan W. Brothers, Assistant State’s Attorneys, of counsel), for the People. PER CURIAM.
